{"id":15007,"date":"2024-01-08T21:26:10","date_gmt":"2024-01-08T14:26:10","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/?p=15007"},"modified":"2024-01-08T21:27:00","modified_gmt":"2024-01-08T14:27:00","slug":"hyundai-palisade-2023-mon-ngon-kho-cuong-trong-phan-khuc-hon-suv-co-lon","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/hyundai-palisade-2023-mon-ngon-kho-cuong-trong-phan-khuc-hon-suv-co-lon\/","title":{"rendered":"Hyundai Palisade 2023: &#8216;M\u00f3n ngon&#8217; kh\u00f3 c\u01b0\u1ee1ng trong ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac h\u01a1n SUV c\u1ee1 l\u1edbn"},"content":{"rendered":"<p class=\"draft_textAlignLeft__3oSdg textAlignLeft_custom\"><strong>Th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng xe \u00f4 t\u00f4 Vi\u1ec7t Nam trong n\u0103m 2023, l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u00e1 g\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u00e3ng xe. \u0110a ph\u1ea7n c\u00e1c m\u1eabu xe d\u00f9 ra m\u1eaft m\u1edbi hay \u0111\u00e3 b\u00e1n \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c h\u00e3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ecb l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 d\u1ec5 ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi ti\u00eau d\u00f9ng. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh h\u1eadu Covid, n\u1ec1n kinh t\u1ebf ch\u01b0a th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i, th\u00ec \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem nh\u01b0 b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111i h\u1eefu hi\u1ec7u gi\u00fap k\u00edch c\u1ea7u ti\u00eau d\u00f9ng.<\/strong><\/p>\n<figure class=\"draft_atomic__1eLF0\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.vnreview.vn\/655360_141218525147769_2284587594022912?wt=f1670f2b810831c1774d1acd72d44058&amp;rt=e2f88d629e3456aae75590a82d933ed6&amp;width=1080\" alt=\"Tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m Hyundai Palisade 2023: 'M\u00f3n ngon' kh\u00f3 c\u01b0\u1ee1ng trong ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac h\u01a1n SUV c\u1ee1 l\u1edbn\" width=\"100%\" \/><\/figure>\n<p class=\"draft_textAlignLeft__3oSdg textAlignLeft_custom\">Hyundai c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng n\u1eb1m ngo\u00e0i \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u01b0\u1edbng tr\u00ean, khi h\u00e3ng \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u m\u1eabu xe Hyundai Palisade th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 m\u1edbi, v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 g\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi ti\u00eau d\u00f9ng. Hyundai Palisade hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e2n ph\u1ed1i v\u1edbi 4 phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n c\u00f9ng m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 t\u1eeb 1.469 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ed3ng (\u0111\u00e3 bao g\u1ed3m thu\u1ebf VAT).<\/p>\n<p class=\"draft_textAlignLeft__3oSdg textAlignLeft_custom\">M\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u00e1 tr\u00ean c\u1ee7a Hyundai \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn t\u1edbi ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac xe SUV h\u1ea1ng E, nh\u01b0ng m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 l\u1ea1i ch\u1ec9 ngang xe \u1edf ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac SUV h\u1ea1ng D. Ngo\u00e0i ra m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u00e1 tr\u00ean c\u0169ng s\u1ebd th\u1ed5i c\u01a1n gi\u00f3 m\u1edbi v\u00e0o ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac xe SUV t\u1ea1i th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng trong n\u01b0\u1edbc.<\/p>\n<p class=\"draft_headerTwo__s5R2O\"><strong>Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i, c\u00e1 t\u00ednh<\/strong><\/p>\n<figure class=\"draft_atomic__1eLF0\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.vnreview.vn\/524288_141218525147770_2284591888990208?wt=3cf85b6a9a687228e37d4a79ceb05bdd&amp;rt=412cd0cde1cb8f15922a9872f19ce1d6&amp;width=1080\" alt=\"Tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m Hyundai Palisade 2023: 'M\u00f3n ngon' kh\u00f3 c\u01b0\u1ee1ng trong ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac h\u01a1n SUV c\u1ee1 l\u1edbn\" width=\"100%\" \/><\/figure>\n<p class=\"draft_textAlignLeft__3oSdg textAlignLeft_custom\">V\u1ec1 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf, Hyundai Palisade s\u1edf h\u1eefu phong c\u00e1ch thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf c\u1ee9ng c\u00e1p, th\u1ef1c d\u1ee5ng v\u00e0 thu h\u00fat. M\u1eb7t tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ee7a xe n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt v\u1edbi l\u01b0\u1edbi t\u1ea3n nhi\u1ec7t h\u00ecnh vu\u00f4ng s\u1eafc c\u1ea1nh t\u1ea1o h\u00ecnh th\u00e1c n\u01b0\u1edbc Cascading Grill.<\/p>\n<p class=\"draft_textAlignLeft__3oSdg textAlignLeft_custom\">Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf l\u01b0\u1edbi t\u1ea3n nhi\u1ec7t n\u00e0y c\u0169ng \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng phong c\u00e1ch kh\u00ed \u0111\u1ed9ng h\u1ecdc tham s\u1ed1 Parametric Dynamics nh\u01b0 Hyundai Tucson, gi\u00fap t\u1ea1o n\u00ean thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf v\u1eefng ch\u00e3i nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t t\u1ea5m khi\u00ean m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd.<\/p>\n<figure class=\"draft_atomic__1eLF0\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.vnreview.vn\/655360_141218525147771_2284596183957504?wt=d84f64d1edc634f174e758c98613a0e0&amp;rt=72d255c18002a18e5c9e1adef0da3ecd&amp;width=1080\" alt=\"Tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m Hyundai Palisade 2023: 'M\u00f3n ngon' kh\u00f3 c\u01b0\u1ee1ng trong ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac h\u01a1n SUV c\u1ee1 l\u1edbn\" width=\"100%\" \/><\/figure>\n<p class=\"draft_textAlignLeft__3oSdg textAlignLeft_custom\">Hai b\u00ean c\u1ee7a \u2018t\u1ea5m khi\u00ean\u2019 l\u00e0 c\u1ee5m \u0111\u00e8n chi\u1ebfu s\u00e1ng d\u1ea1ng LED \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb7t d\u1ecdc mang thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf T-Shape t\u1ea1o c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c b\u1ec1 th\u1ebf d\u00e0nh cho xe<\/p>\n<figure class=\"draft_atomic__1eLF0\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.vnreview.vn\/851968_141218525147772_2284600478924800?wt=1b76559519d8f9c801af176b4deea512&amp;rt=b8bd66070b3cffab4517dc43ce4d3f22&amp;width=1080\" alt=\"Tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m Hyundai Palisade 2023: 'M\u00f3n ngon' kh\u00f3 c\u01b0\u1ee1ng trong ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac h\u01a1n SUV c\u1ee1 l\u1edbn\" width=\"100%\" \/><\/figure>\n<p class=\"draft_textAlignLeft__3oSdg textAlignLeft_custom\">B\u01b0\u1edbc sang t\u1edbi th\u00e2n xe, nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 chia s\u1ebb \u1edf tr\u00ean Hyundai Palisade s\u1edf h\u1eefu k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc chi\u1ec1u d\u00e0i x r\u1ed9ng x cao l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00e0 4.995 mm x 1.975 mm x 1.750 mm, v\u1edbi chi\u1ec1u d\u00e0i c\u01a1 s\u1edf 2.900m gi\u00fap cho m\u1eabu xe n\u00e0y b\u1ec1 th\u1ebf v\u00e0 to l\u1edbn ngang ng\u1eeda c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 trong c\u00f9ng ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac. Nh\u1edd c\u00e1ch thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf tr\u00ean, c\u0169ng gi\u00fap cho khoang n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Hyundai Palisade r\u1ed9ng r\u00e3i \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3.<\/p>\n<p class=\"draft_headerTwo__s5R2O\"><strong>Kh\u00f4ng gian n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t \u201c\u0103n, ch\u01a1i\u201d<\/strong><\/p>\n<figure class=\"draft_atomic__1eLF0\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.vnreview.vn\/720896_141218525147773_2284604773892096?wt=c7dcbd94c50e2c6f01e484dd973ced8f&amp;rt=b1899f7fb8e3653781b7e3494ada445a&amp;width=1080\" alt=\"Tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m Hyundai Palisade 2023: 'M\u00f3n ngon' kh\u00f3 c\u01b0\u1ee1ng trong ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac h\u01a1n SUV c\u1ee1 l\u1edbn\" width=\"100%\" \/><\/figure>\n<p class=\"draft_textAlignLeft__3oSdg textAlignLeft_custom\">C\u00e1c th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u xe H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i cu\u1ed9c ch\u01a1i v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng g\u00f3i trang b\u1ecb d\u00e0nh cho ch\u1ee7 xe. Hyundai Palisade l\u00e0 m\u1eabu xe minh ch\u1ee9ng r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng cho \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y, khi h\u00e3ng xe H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c r\u1ea5t h\u00e0o ph\u00f3ng trang b\u1ecb h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i, sang tr\u1ecdng d\u00e0nh cho xe.<\/p>\n<p class=\"draft_textAlignLeft__3oSdg textAlignLeft_custom\">Nh\u1edd thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf ngo\u1ea1i th\u1ea5t b\u1ec1 th\u1ebf, to l\u1edbn gi\u00fap cho kh\u00f4ng gian n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Palisade tr\u1edf n\u00ean v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng r\u1ed9ng r\u00e3i, ngay c\u1ea3 \u1edf h\u00e0ng gh\u1ebf th\u1ee9 3. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng Vi\u1ec7t Nam, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean d\u00f9ng xe v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch di chuy\u1ec3n gia \u0111\u00ecnh.<\/p>\n<figure class=\"draft_atomic__1eLF0\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.vnreview.vn\/720896_141218525147774_2284609068859392?wt=bc0b3060d044d3fa861cbc5379a871bf&amp;rt=bebeb3728a6dfaa1d5d2ceb7dd90e9c6&amp;width=1080\" alt=\"Tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m Hyundai Palisade 2023: 'M\u00f3n ngon' kh\u00f3 c\u01b0\u1ee1ng trong ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac h\u01a1n SUV c\u1ee1 l\u1edbn\" width=\"100%\" \/><\/figure>\n<p class=\"draft_textAlignLeft__3oSdg textAlignLeft_custom\">Ngo\u00e0i kh\u00f4ng gian n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t r\u1ed9ng r\u00e3i, Hyundai Palisade t\u00edch h\u1ee3p l\u00ean h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 ch\u1ee7 xe nh\u01b0 m\u00e0n trung t\u00e2m k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc 12,3 inch, k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i camera 360 \u0111\u1ed9, h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 Apple CarPlay\/Android Auto, m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh HUD, phanh tay \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1eed.<\/p>\n<figure class=\"draft_atomic__1eLF0\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.vnreview.vn\/524288_141218525147775_2284613363826688?wt=0b86a094764b46aefefee27cbd6b423a&amp;rt=178de7833d65a2f96aabffa8cb060130&amp;width=1080\" alt=\"Tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m Hyundai Palisade 2023: 'M\u00f3n ngon' kh\u00f3 c\u01b0\u1ee1ng trong ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac h\u01a1n SUV c\u1ee1 l\u1edbn\" width=\"100%\" \/><\/figure>\n<p class=\"draft_textAlignLeft__3oSdg textAlignLeft_custom\">V\u00f4 l\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed5i giao di\u1ec7n t\u1eeb 3 l\u00ean 4 ch\u1ea5u, ph\u00eda sau l\u00e0 b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u1ed3 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt s\u1ed1 m\u1edbi k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc 10 inch. H\u1ed1c gi\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00f2a nay m\u1ea3nh h\u01a1n nh\u01b0ng d\u00e0n \u0111\u1ec1u theo chi\u1ec1u ngang t\u00e1p l\u00f4. B\u1ea3n Exclusive s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng gh\u1ebf b\u1ecdc da, c\u00f2n b\u1ea3n Prestige trang b\u1ecb gh\u1ebf da Nappa.<\/p>\n<p class=\"draft_textAlignLeft__3oSdg textAlignLeft_custom\">L\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u1eabu xe d\u00e0nh cho gia \u0111\u00ecnh, Hyundai Palisade \u0111\u1eb7t s\u1ef1 ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf gh\u1ebf, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 gh\u1ebf l\u00e1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf theo phong c\u00e1ch c\u00f4ng th\u00e1i h\u1ecdc, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 tr\u00ean c\u00e1c m\u1eabu xe sang c\u1ee7a Genesis. Lo\u1ea1i gh\u1ebf n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed1i \u01b0u h\u00f3a \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3m m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi ng\u1ed3i trong su\u1ed1t qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh di chuy\u1ec3n.<\/p>\n<figure class=\"draft_atomic__1eLF0\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.vnreview.vn\/720896_141218525147776_2284617658793984?wt=1445d5860f3585e609eb5aafea15c534&amp;rt=5d74d676aa03f031e7cfc78868a7e0a9&amp;width=1080\" alt=\"Tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m Hyundai Palisade 2023: 'M\u00f3n ngon' kh\u00f3 c\u01b0\u1ee1ng trong ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac h\u01a1n SUV c\u1ee1 l\u1edbn\" width=\"100%\" \/><\/figure>\n<p class=\"draft_textAlignLeft__3oSdg textAlignLeft_custom\">Ngo\u00e0i ra, c\u1ea3 gh\u1ebf h\u00e0ng 1 v\u00e0 h\u00e0ng 2 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trang b\u1ecb t\u00ednh n\u0103ng l\u00e0m m\u00e1t v\u00e0 s\u01b0\u1edfi \u1ea5m, t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i c\u1ea3 trong \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n th\u1eddi ti\u1ebft n\u1eafng n\u00f3ng hay l\u1ea1nh bu\u1ed1t. T\u1ef1a \u0111\u1ea7u m\u1edbi v\u00e0 t\u1ef1a tay c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u00f3c \u0111\u1ed9, t\u1ed1i \u01b0u h\u00f3a s\u1ef1 tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi ng\u1ed3i.<\/p>\n<p class=\"draft_textAlignLeft__3oSdg textAlignLeft_custom\">Gh\u1ebf h\u00e0ng 2 c\u00f2n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn c\u1ea5u h\u00ecnh 2 ch\u1ed7 ki\u1ec3u th\u01b0\u01a1ng gia ho\u1eb7c 3 ch\u1ed7 gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 c\u00e1c m\u1eabu xe th\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng. C\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh m\u1ed9t ch\u1ea1m gi\u00fap vi\u1ec7c thay \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1ecb tr\u00ed gh\u1ebf tr\u1edf n\u00ean d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng v\u00e0 thu\u1eadn ti\u1ec7n, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t h\u1eefu \u00edch khi c\u1ea7n di chuy\u1ec3n l\u00ean xu\u1ed1ng h\u00e0ng gh\u1ebf th\u1ee9 3.<\/p>\n<p class=\"draft_headerTwo__s5R2O\"><strong>Tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m l\u00e1i<\/strong><\/p>\n<figure class=\"draft_atomic__1eLF0\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.vnreview.vn\/655360_141218525147778_2284621953761280?wt=b59213f1fb2683b1346df69820ac2d47&amp;rt=6e456d7dc1cce0f2146dd24d9c26263b&amp;width=1080\" alt=\"Tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m Hyundai Palisade 2023: 'M\u00f3n ngon' kh\u00f3 c\u01b0\u1ee1ng trong ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac h\u01a1n SUV c\u1ee1 l\u1edbn\" width=\"100%\" \/><\/figure>\n<p class=\"draft_textAlignLeft__3oSdg textAlignLeft_custom\">T\u1ea1m r\u1eddi xa c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c \u0111\u00e1nh l\u00e1i c\u1ee7a v\u00f4-l\u0103ng, m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eed t\u0103ng t\u1ed1c tr\u00ean nhi\u1ec1u c\u00e1c \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00e1c nhau v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec1u cho th\u1ea5y \u0111\u1ed9 tr\u1ec5 ch\u00e2n ga tr\u00ean Palisade \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi tr\u00ean Hyundai Santa Fe ra m\u1eaft tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, khi chuy\u1ec3n sang ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 Sport th\u00ec c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c t\u0103ng t\u1ed1c th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 r\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<\/p>\n<p class=\"draft_textAlignLeft__3oSdg textAlignLeft_custom\">V\u1ec1 tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m l\u00e1i, \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean n\u1eb1m \u1edf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u00e1ch \u00e2m c\u1ee7a xe. Th\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng xe s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 d\u1ea7u, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf c\u00e1ch \u00e2m t\u1ed1t, s\u1ebd d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn g\u00e2y ra ti\u1ebfng \u1ed3n t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00e0o trong khoang l\u00e1i. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Hyundai kh\u1eafc ph\u1ee5c kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t, n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 ch\u00fa \u00fd, g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng nghe th\u1ea5y \u00e2m thanh t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1edbi t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 d\u1ea7u 2.2L.<\/p>\n<p class=\"draft_textAlignLeft__3oSdg textAlignLeft_custom\">Ngo\u00e0i ra, nh\u01b0 \u0111a ph\u1ea7n \u0111\u1eb7c tr\u01b0ng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c d\u00f2ng xe Hyundai, ph\u1ea7n v\u00f4-l\u0103ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf kh\u00e1 nh\u1eb9 khi di chuy\u1ec3n \u1edf t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 th\u1ea5p v\u00e0 si\u1ebft ch\u1eb7t \u1edf t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 cao. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y gi\u00fap ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e1i t\u0103ng s\u1ef1 linh ho\u1ea1t khi di chuy\u1ec3n tr\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng.<\/p>\n<figure class=\"draft_atomic__1eLF0\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.vnreview.vn\/851968_141218525147779_2284626248728576?wt=ddb0515fb322bccad1a476b0e08116f0&amp;rt=3ce85df8c7f0f9baf088a3cccff5dae6&amp;width=1080\" alt=\"Tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m Hyundai Palisade 2023: 'M\u00f3n ngon' kh\u00f3 c\u01b0\u1ee1ng trong ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac h\u01a1n SUV c\u1ee1 l\u1edbn\" width=\"100%\" \/><\/figure>\n<p class=\"draft_textAlignLeft__3oSdg textAlignLeft_custom\">Palisade th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 m\u1edbi trang b\u1ecb h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng treo \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1eed t\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u00edch v\u1edbi 4 ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 l\u00e1i, \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y gi\u00fap mang l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i v\u00e0 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1ed1i \u0111a cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e1i v\u00e0 h\u00e0nh kh\u00e1ch. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e1i th\u1eed xe tr\u00ean nhi\u1ec1u lo\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ecba h\u00ecnh kh\u00e1c nhau, t\u1eeb \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u1ef1a \u00eam \u00e1i \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng g\u1ed3 gh\u1ec1 nh\u01b0ng h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng phu\u1ed9c c\u1ee7a xe ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi ng\u1ed3i ph\u00eda sau v\u1eabn c\u00f3 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i d\u00f9 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ecba h\u00ecnh kh\u00f3.<\/p>\n<figure class=\"draft_atomic__1eLF0\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.vnreview.vn\/917504_141218525147780_2284630543695872?wt=c778134e4484604036342d53445a2e38&amp;rt=1f60d16731ee40914174a338f7541790&amp;width=1080\" alt=\"Tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m Hyundai Palisade 2023: 'M\u00f3n ngon' kh\u00f3 c\u01b0\u1ee1ng trong ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac h\u01a1n SUV c\u1ee1 l\u1edbn\" width=\"100%\" \/><\/figure>\n<p class=\"draft_textAlignLeft__3oSdg textAlignLeft_custom\">V\u1ec1 kh\u00eda c\u1ea1nh an to\u00e0n, Hyundai Palisade \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trang b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 c\u00e1c c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 an to\u00e0n th\u1ee5 \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng. C\u00e1c t\u00ednh n\u0103ng an to\u00e0n thu\u1ed9c di\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 trong ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac v\u1edbi c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1eed, ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t l\u1ef1c k\u00e9o, h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 kh\u1edfi h\u00e0nh ngang d\u1ed1c, c\u1ea3m bi\u1ebfn \u00e1p su\u1ea5t l\u1ed1p, 7 t\u00fai kh\u00ed v\u00e0 g\u00f3i h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 l\u00e1i n\u00e2ng cao Hyundai SmartSense.<\/p>\n<p class=\"draft_textAlignLeft__3oSdg textAlignLeft_custom\">Trong l\u1ea7n tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m n\u00e0y, do ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1eed c\u00e1c t\u00ednh n\u0103ng an to\u00e0n c\u1ee7a xe. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u1edf bu\u1ed5i ra m\u1eaft xe t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eed v\u00e0 th\u1ea5y r\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c t\u00ednh n\u0103ng an to\u00e0n c\u1ee7a xe ho\u1ea1t t\u1ed1t \u1edf nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n kh\u00e1c nhau.<\/p>\n<p class=\"draft_headerTwo__s5R2O\"><strong>T\u1ed5ng k\u1ebft<\/strong><\/p>\n<figure class=\"draft_atomic__1eLF0\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.vnreview.vn\/917504_141218525147782_2284639133630464?wt=f80ce1777fc0e9285b3dc5c408e0c6a9&amp;rt=2b50cfb3ce9bfa09526574c168af1e4e&amp;width=1080\" alt=\"Tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m Hyundai Palisade 2023: 'M\u00f3n ngon' kh\u00f3 c\u01b0\u1ee1ng trong ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac h\u01a1n SUV c\u1ee1 l\u1edbn\" width=\"100%\" \/><\/figure>\n<p class=\"draft_textAlignLeft__3oSdg textAlignLeft_custom\">V\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 t\u1eeb 1,4 t\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ed9ng Hyundai Palisade mang t\u1edbi cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi ti\u00eau d\u00f9ng chi\u1ebfc xe n\u1eb1m ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac E v\u1edbi thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf ngo\u1ea1i th\u1ea5t h\u1ea7m h\u1ed1, sang tr\u1ecdng, k\u00e8m theo \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng gian n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t r\u1ed9ng r\u00e3i gi\u00fap \u0111em t\u1edbi tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m t\u1ed1t d\u00e0nh cho c\u1ea3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e1i v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi ng\u1ed3i ph\u00eda sau.<\/p>\n<p class=\"draft_textAlignLeft__3oSdg textAlignLeft_custom\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, Palisade th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 m\u1edbi c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trang b\u1ecb h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7, t\u00ednh n\u0103ng cao c\u1ea5p t\u1ea1o c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i kh\u00f3 l\u00f2ng c\u00f3 m\u1eabu xe n\u00e0o trong c\u00f9ng ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac s\u00e1nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.<\/p>\n<p class=\"draft_textAlignLeft__3oSdg textAlignLeft_custom\">Xe c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd, \u00eam \u00e1i v\u00e0 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh, c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng treo hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i. N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n \u0111ang t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfc SUV 7 ch\u1ed7 h\u1ea1ng sang, Palisade 2023 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng xe \u00f4 t\u00f4 Vi\u1ec7t Nam trong n\u0103m 2023, l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u00e1 g\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u00e3ng xe. \u0110a ph\u1ea7n c\u00e1c m\u1eabu xe d\u00f9 ra m\u1eaft m\u1edbi hay \u0111\u00e3 b\u00e1n \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c h\u00e3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ecb l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 d\u1ec5 ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi ti\u00eau [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":15008,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[30],"tags":[52,66,34],"yst_prominent_words":[],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/15007"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=15007"}],"version-history":[{"count":2,"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/15007\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":15010,"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/15007\/revisions\/15010"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/15008"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=15007"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=15007"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=15007"},{"taxonomy":"yst_prominent_words","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/yst_prominent_words?